{{中华人民共和国军事}}

'''中國海上民兵'''是对[[中華人民共和國政府|中华人民共和国政府]]资助海上民兵的指控<ref name="China_fishermen_mercenaries">{{cite news |last=Thomas |first=Jason |title=China’s ‘fishermen’ mercenaries |url=https://www.theaustralian.com.au/commentary/chinas-military-funds-and-trains-hundreds-of-fishermen-to-challenge-us/news-story/4f2309bc95c3fa9dffd072c95adc4ccc |newspaper=The Weekend Australian |date=2020-09-02 |accessdate=2020-09-05 |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515184622/https://www.theaustralian.com.au/subscribe/news/1/?sourceCode=TAWEB_WRE170_a&dest=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theaustralian.com.au%2Fcommentary%2Fchinas-military-funds-and-trains-hundreds-of-fishermen-to-challenge-us%2Fnews-story%2F4f2309bc95c3fa9dffd072c95adc4ccc&memtype=anonymous&mode=premium&nk=525c773ed5885ee51010646f8c7bd188-1621104381 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，据称以'''武裝漁船'''方式為外界所認識。

== 观点 ==
武装渔船队是中国力量投射的一部分<ref name="China_fishermen_mercenaries" />，部署渔船是为了控制有争议海上领土、海岛（包括[[南海|南海]]、[[釣魚臺列嶼|钓鱼台列屿]]等）。由于在[[南海|南海]]活动时没有明确的身份标识，他们有时被{{谁？}}称为 「小蓝人」{{NoteTag|这个词是[[海军战争学院|海军战争学院]]的安德鲁·S·埃里克森创造的，指的是俄罗斯在2014年[[俄羅斯合併克里米亞|吞并克里米亚]]期间的「[[小綠人_(格魯烏)|小绿人]]」。}}<ref>{{cite web |title=Analysis: What's so fishy about China's 'maritime militia'? |url=https://monitoring.bbc.co.uk/product/c200r2cr |access-date=25 July 2020 |date=15 April 2019 |last=Jakhar |first=Pratik |publisher=BBC Monitoring |website=monitoring.bbc.co.uk |archive-date=2021-05-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515184551/https://monitoring.bbc.co.uk/product/c200r2cr |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

